  m_Name: D4E1 Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 0
  lines:
  - "H\u2026. heyy man! D-documents,uh, yeah I got them riiiiiiight\u2026.. here!"
  - "You give \u2018em a goooood look through, like a REALLL good look through, yeah?"
  - "Buuut I\u2019ll tell you ONE thing ok\u2026. just one thing, ONE thing. All
    this shit makes NO sense man, I\u2019m telling you."
  - "NONE of these signs of this illness thingy add up, wheres the link between ANY
    of those \u201Csymptoms or whatever\u201D"
  - And it came from those oogly boogly green aliens from the stars?
  - "Those don\u2019t exist man! I tell you what, I thiiiink\u2026 They\u2019re making
    something up! Everything is a liiiieeeee! "
  - "Soooo in conclusion\u2026.. THEY\u2019RE THE REAL ALIENS!!!"
  - "So you\u2019re working for aliens, man. That\u2019s fucckked up! You gotta stop
    man\u2026.. "
